headline.main: Warehouse Group Joins Foreign Traders In Opposition to Lease-Lend Methods

lead_paragraph: Warehousemen joined with foreign traders generally in expressing indignation yesterday over the disclosure of the memorandum by a government official setting forth a proposed extension of lease-lend practices which the traders have currently been protesting.
abstract: Warehousemen's Assn of Port of N Y joins forwarders and exporters in protest
